  "text": "We also observed foxo3b expression showing a similar, stochastic dynamic during blastula and gastrula stages ( Figure S3O -H'). This is in contrast with the quasi-ubiquitous expression described before [CITATION_1] , however, repeated experiments yielded the same results. Of note, though expression seemed stochastic both in wild type and ich embryos, the overall expression appeared higher in wild types during early stages of development.",
